      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must cover the operating range (flow rate 2–6 L/min, speed 2500–4500 RPM) representative of CPB clinical use.",
      "rationale": "Validation dataset spans 2–5 L/min and 2500–4500 RPM, encompassing the clinically relevant CPB operating envelope. Required level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
