      "rationale": "Blood viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s) and density (1060 kg/m3) taken from published standards. Hemolysis power-law constants from Giersiepen et al. Formal sensitivity analysis not required at MRL 2. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3."
