      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; documented mapping of experimental to simulation boundary conditions is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Boundary condition mapping between experimental setup and CFD model is documented in simulation report Appendix B. Formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3."
