    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for the declared model risk level. The CFD hemolysis prediction model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the operating envelope described in the bound requirement and claim. No weakeners identified that would reduce confidence below the acceptance threshold.",
